# Addon Feature Sync (unix-monitor ↔ synology-monitor)

When adding or modifying features in **one** addon (unix-monitor or synology-monitor):

1. **Check compatibility** – Verify the feature can work in both contexts (Synology DSM/SPK vs generic Unix).
2. **After compatibility is confirmed** – Ask the user: *"Should this feature be added to the other addon as well?"*
3. Do not blindly port – Some features differ by design (e.g., Synology has no script-based self-update; use Package Center).
